data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Abingdon, VA! This exquisite property has been meticulously remodeled and boasts nearly 2,800 square feet of luxurious living space. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by spacious living rooms adorned with a cozy fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxing evenings. The dining area seamlessly flows into a stunning, well-appointed kitchen featuring granite countertops, elegant two-tone cabinets, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances.  Downstairs, discover a tranquil haven where you can unwind and find peace after a long day. This level offers three generously sized bedrooms, with the potential for a fourth bedroom if needed. The primary bedroom has been thoughtfully expanded to include an adjoining room transformed into a dream closet space, providing ample storage for your wardrobe essentials.
